tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE shared_documents (
    document_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    document_name STRING,
    upload_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    contributor_name STRING,
    file_location STRING
)

CREATE TABLE Documents (
    document_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    document_name STRING,
    document_content STRING,
    created_by_user_id UUID,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE shared_documents (document_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	 document_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
	 author VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
	 creation_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
	 document_content TEXT NOT NULL,
	 collaborators JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE presentations (presentation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	 presentation_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
	 presenter VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
	 presentation_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
	 slides JSONB,
	 viewers JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE files (file_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	 file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
	 file_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
	 uploader VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
	 upload_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
	 file_content BYTEA,
	 permissions JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE Presentations (
    presentation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    presentation_name VARCHAR(255),
    created_by VARCHAR(100),
    created_at TIMESTAMP,
    thumbnail_url VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE Files (
    file_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255),
    file_type VARCHAR(50),
    size_in_bytes INT,
    uploaded_by VARCHAR(100),
    uploaded_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    description VARCHAR(500),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    team_lead VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE Users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(100),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    role VARCHAR(50),
    join_date DATE
);
